---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="About Us | The Life Insider"
  description="The Life Insider helps shoppers make smarter buying decisions with data-driven product rankings built from verified customer reviews."
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-narrow prose">
      <div class="kicker">About</div>
      <h1>About The Life Insider</h1>

      <p class="lede">
        Buying well shouldn't require a weekend of research. We built The
        Life Insider to compress hours of comparison work into a single,
        honest, data-backed page.
      </p>

      <h2>The problem we solve</h2>
      <p>
        For almost any product you want to buy, there are hundreds of options,
        thousands of scattered reviews, and dozens of "top 10" lists that
        never explain where their rankings come from. Most shoppers end up
        doing one of two things: spending hours cross-referencing reviews, or
        gambling on the first result they see.
      </p>

      <h2>Our approach</h2>
      <p>
        We do the cross-referencing for you — systematically. Our team
        aggregates verified customer ratings and review volumes, compares
        specifications and pricing, and evaluates warranty and returns
        protection across the leading products in each category. The result is
        the <strong>Insider Score</strong>: a single number out of 10, built
        from evidence, with the methodology published for anyone to read in
        <a href="/how-we-rate/">How We Rate</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>How we keep it honest</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Our scores start from what verified buyers actually report — never from what brands tell us.</li>
        <li>We publish our rating methodology and our <a href="/advertising-disclosure/">Advertising Disclosure</a> in plain English.</li>
        <li>We update our rankings as prices, availability, and review data change, and every page shows its last-updated date.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How we make money</h2>
      <p>
        When you purchase through links on our site, we may earn an affiliate
        commission at no extra cost to you. That's the entire business model —
        no paywalls, no selling your data, no charging brands to alter scores.
        Full details: <a href="/advertising-disclosure/">Advertising Disclosure</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Get in touch</h2>
      <p>
        Questions, corrections, or partnership inquiries:
        <a href="/contact/">contact us here</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
